WEBVTT

00:00:57.745 --> 00:00:58.705
Is that…

00:01:06.880 --> 00:01:07.755
No way.

00:01:14.179 --> 00:01:16.764
GREETINGS, DEAR SUBSCRIBER

00:01:44.709 --> 00:01:45.543
You made it?

00:01:46.669 --> 00:01:47.503
Who are you?

00:01:49.589 --> 00:01:51.341
Let's see.

00:01:53.051 --> 00:01:56.763
Seo Mi-rae, 29, heterosexual.

00:01:57.972 --> 00:01:58.806
Right?

00:02:00.391 --> 00:02:01.392
Yes.

00:02:01.893 --> 00:02:04.520
Would you happen to be an actual person?

00:02:05.188 --> 00:02:08.983
I'm your designated dating manager.
Call me Unni if you want.

00:02:11.945 --> 00:02:16.199
But where are we?
I mean, what's with all those posters?

00:02:17.825 --> 00:02:18.993
Just a sec.

00:02:33.383 --> 00:02:34.509
Your hand.

00:02:38.096 --> 00:02:40.640
Those who come here
are each given this ring.

00:02:41.307 --> 00:02:44.060
It'll appear on you automatically
every time you log in.

00:02:44.143 --> 00:02:45.853
Take it off, and you'll log out.

00:02:46.646 --> 00:02:50.525
So you're saying this place
is a virtual reality, aren't you?

00:02:51.192 --> 00:02:52.485
Yeah.

00:02:53.361 --> 00:02:55.571
What about me? Is my body safe at home?

00:02:56.489 --> 00:02:57.323
Probably?

00:03:09.002 --> 00:03:10.962
All right. Let's get going now.

00:03:11.838 --> 00:03:12.672
Where to?

00:03:24.309 --> 00:03:26.227
THE MAN YOU THINK YOU KNOW

00:03:26.311 --> 00:03:27.312
Enter.

00:03:28.396 --> 00:03:29.439
What?

00:03:58.343 --> 00:03:59.177
What the…

00:04:02.764 --> 00:04:03.723
Wait a second.

00:04:07.727 --> 00:04:10.521
This is Choi Si-woo.

00:04:14.359 --> 00:04:18.154
Congratulations, Ms. Seo Mi-rae,
on meeting your first date!

00:04:31.334 --> 00:04:33.127
I can't believe how handsome he is.

00:04:41.219 --> 00:04:43.137
Are you okay?

00:04:46.557 --> 00:04:47.767
Oh my God!

00:04:49.143 --> 00:04:50.144
Who…

00:04:53.689 --> 00:04:56.109
Take it off, and you'll log out.

00:05:16.421 --> 00:05:18.589
EPISODE 2
CLICHE OR CLASSIC

00:05:19.257 --> 00:05:20.425
BOYFRIEND ON DEMAND

00:05:21.217 --> 00:05:24.887
DU showcases its technology.
Experience BoD with all five senses.

00:05:24.971 --> 00:05:28.015
Boyfriend on Demand,
coming soon to redefine romance.

00:05:28.099 --> 00:05:29.392
Concerns over addiction.

00:05:32.520 --> 00:05:36.357
When the door to everyday life closes,
a new door opens,

00:05:36.899 --> 00:05:39.902
and the date
you've been dreaming of begins.

00:05:40.528 --> 00:05:41.863
Ready for another dreamy day?

00:05:43.614 --> 00:05:46.868
This is a place where any romance
you desire becomes reality.

00:05:47.493 --> 00:05:50.246
There are 900 themes just for you.

00:05:50.746 --> 00:05:54.041
So who will you be dating today?

00:06:04.719 --> 00:06:06.721
Min Jun-young, you bastard.

00:06:08.639 --> 00:06:10.183
I respect the hell out of you.

00:06:19.692 --> 00:06:21.903
When you experience something surreal,

00:06:22.695 --> 00:06:24.780
it takes time to process it.

00:06:42.924 --> 00:06:43.966
Ms. Seo.

00:06:49.055 --> 00:06:51.098
Dong-min told me to bring this to you.

00:06:53.267 --> 00:06:56.020
Oh, right. You can leave it there.

00:06:56.103 --> 00:06:58.022
-I'll put it here.
-Yeah.

00:07:09.617 --> 00:07:12.912
What? You want to move
Hwany's webtoon to Fridays?

00:07:12.995 --> 00:07:14.288
Take a look at this.

00:07:14.789 --> 00:07:18.793
It's the list of our Friday webtoons.
Don't you think it's outdated?

00:07:18.876 --> 00:07:21.546
And just look at the ratings
for The Man to Know.

00:07:21.629 --> 00:07:22.505
It's hopeless.

00:07:22.588 --> 00:07:25.091
But Hwany's really catching on.

00:07:25.174 --> 00:07:27.885
I doubt he'd want to compete with Ms. Yun.

00:07:27.969 --> 00:07:30.471
That's why you should just
float the idea to him.

00:07:31.931 --> 00:07:33.766
What's wrong? You don't want to?

00:07:34.976 --> 00:07:36.269
No, it's not that.

00:07:37.061 --> 00:07:38.646
I just don't see why

00:07:38.729 --> 00:07:41.691
you'd have two popular authors
competing on the same day.

00:07:41.774 --> 00:07:45.027
I have no intention of betting
this company's fate on one person.

00:07:45.778 --> 00:07:48.781
Hwany does everything
you tell him to do anyway.

00:07:48.864 --> 00:07:51.867
Just mention it to him, okay?

00:07:52.368 --> 00:07:53.286
Well?

00:07:55.413 --> 00:07:57.123
Sure. I'll do that.

00:07:57.206 --> 00:07:58.332
Okay.

00:07:58.416 --> 00:08:00.835
-All right. Get back to work.
-Yes, sir.

00:08:04.672 --> 00:08:05.506
Sir?

00:08:06.882 --> 00:08:09.051
Is Seo Mi-rae also aware of this?

00:08:09.135 --> 00:08:10.761
She doesn't need to know.

00:08:10.845 --> 00:08:12.972
If Yun Song finds out, we'll be done for!

00:08:13.598 --> 00:08:15.808
We'll act first, think later.

00:08:17.643 --> 00:08:18.561
I see.

00:08:23.774 --> 00:08:26.110
This is uncomfortable.

00:08:33.075 --> 00:08:34.702
It's just a drawing.

00:08:35.202 --> 00:08:36.329
Get a grip.

00:08:58.934 --> 00:09:01.062
NAEMO'S BEST FRIDAY WEBTOON
THE MAN TO KNOW

00:09:02.730 --> 00:09:04.315
Was this here before?

00:09:08.611 --> 00:09:09.612
CAN I… STAY THE NIGHT?

00:09:11.072 --> 00:09:12.156
What?

00:09:20.665 --> 00:09:22.750
WANT A SHARPER NOSE THAN A WEBTOON LEAD?
PEOPLE PLASTIC SURGERY

00:09:22.833 --> 00:09:23.959
Isn't Choi Si-woo so cool?

00:09:24.043 --> 00:09:25.378
I know, right?

00:09:27.380 --> 00:09:28.297
THE MAN TO KNOW

00:09:31.092 --> 00:09:32.134
THE MAN TO KNOW

00:09:34.095 --> 00:09:35.346
THE MAN TO KNOW, VOL. 1

00:09:39.934 --> 00:09:41.268
Everywhere I look,

00:09:42.103 --> 00:09:43.312
there's Choi Si-woo.

00:09:51.570 --> 00:09:54.949
THE MAN TO KNOW
NAEMO'S NO. 1 WEBTOON IN STORES

00:10:35.156 --> 00:10:37.450
What? Where am I?

00:10:52.548 --> 00:10:55.426
Eun Na-ra, the female lead
of The Man to Know, is a hotelier.

00:10:57.344 --> 00:11:01.140
Am I supposed to experience the life
of a female lead in a webtoon?

00:11:07.855 --> 00:11:09.523
APPROVAL REQUEST

00:11:09.607 --> 00:11:10.941
"General manager"?

00:11:26.791 --> 00:11:29.084
GENERAL MANAGER CHOI SI-WOO

00:11:31.337 --> 00:11:32.463
It really is him.

00:11:34.298 --> 00:11:36.133
He really was Choi Si-woo.

00:11:41.430 --> 00:11:45.142
It appears an employee had the nerve
to sit on my desk.

00:11:46.936 --> 00:11:47.895
Was I seeing things?

00:11:49.355 --> 00:11:51.565
-No, it's just--
-Get out. Now.

00:12:02.368 --> 00:12:03.244
What's his problem?

00:12:04.662 --> 00:12:05.663
Wait.

00:12:14.964 --> 00:12:16.632
I thought you wanted me to leave.

00:12:18.592 --> 00:12:20.177
Have we met before?

00:12:21.971 --> 00:12:23.138
There it is.

00:12:41.824 --> 00:12:44.243
Oh my God. This is insane!

00:12:52.543 --> 00:12:56.130
You, you must be from…

00:12:57.423 --> 00:12:58.340
That's right.

00:12:59.884 --> 00:13:01.302
But how are you here?

00:13:03.053 --> 00:13:05.097
Because I work here?

00:13:08.601 --> 00:13:10.102
I finally found you.

00:13:11.228 --> 00:13:14.565
Ever since the day you saved me…

00:13:16.567 --> 00:13:19.403
not a day has gone by
without me thinking of you.

00:13:19.987 --> 00:13:21.572
Wait, what's he doing?

00:13:21.655 --> 00:13:23.032
I never forgot about you

00:13:24.783 --> 00:13:26.201
for a single moment.

00:13:27.703 --> 00:13:29.330
I had forgotten

00:13:29.413 --> 00:13:32.708
how cheesy The Man to Know was.

00:13:33.709 --> 00:13:36.128
That's sweet,
but that came out of nowhere--

00:13:36.211 --> 00:13:37.046
Wait.

00:13:38.422 --> 00:13:40.007
Let me look for just a moment.

00:13:41.091 --> 00:13:41.926
Look at what?

00:13:43.761 --> 00:13:44.637
It's here.

00:13:47.097 --> 00:13:47.932
What is?

00:13:49.099 --> 00:13:50.809
The face I've been longing for

00:13:51.894 --> 00:13:55.314
and desperately searching for
in my dreams…

00:13:58.651 --> 00:13:59.777
every night.

00:14:07.493 --> 00:14:08.535
Oh shit!

00:14:11.789 --> 00:14:14.667
Is he deranged?
That's more cringe than anyone can handle.

00:14:25.135 --> 00:14:26.095
It's here.

00:14:26.595 --> 00:14:28.180
The face I've been longing for

00:14:28.263 --> 00:14:32.101
and desperately searching for
in my dreams every night.

00:14:32.685 --> 00:14:33.519
I can't take this.

00:14:39.900 --> 00:14:41.318
Can't stand the sight of him?

00:14:42.319 --> 00:14:44.947
Such disrespect
for a hero going off to war.

00:14:45.447 --> 00:14:46.281
Poor Si-woo.

00:14:47.199 --> 00:14:49.034
War? What are you on about?

00:14:49.994 --> 00:14:52.454
-You haven't seen Hwany's Instagram?
-Nope. Why?

00:14:53.539 --> 00:14:54.915
Yikes.

00:14:54.999 --> 00:14:55.833
What?

00:15:02.339 --> 00:15:05.634
Sir, is it true that Hwany's new title
will now be updated every Friday?

00:15:06.593 --> 00:15:07.428
Yes, it is.

00:15:07.511 --> 00:15:10.556
-You can't do that without telling me--
-Hey, you're not my boss!

00:15:10.639 --> 00:15:12.683
Hwany's a big name. You should've told me!

00:15:12.766 --> 00:15:15.602
It's been a while since Yun Song
had some healthy competition.

00:15:15.686 --> 00:15:18.188
This is a good thing. It's for the best.

00:15:20.816 --> 00:15:22.276
Was this, by chance,

00:15:23.819 --> 00:15:26.113
proposed by Producer Park?

00:15:29.533 --> 00:15:30.367
No.

00:15:35.831 --> 00:15:36.749
It really wasn't.

00:15:37.541 --> 00:15:39.168
It's not strong enough.

00:15:44.256 --> 00:15:46.675
The ending has to be more impactful.

00:15:47.176 --> 00:15:49.261
This is as impactful as it gets.

00:15:50.012 --> 00:15:52.222
I might really top the chart at this rate.

00:15:52.306 --> 00:15:53.891
You're daydreaming again.

00:15:54.516 --> 00:15:55.642
Okay.

00:15:55.726 --> 00:15:59.813
If I'm going to make it more impactful,
I'll have to speed up the early scenes.

00:16:00.314 --> 00:16:03.984
And the manager scene in the next episode,
why don't we move it up a little?

00:16:20.334 --> 00:16:22.086
Come on.

00:16:22.753 --> 00:16:25.047
I told you to pick up right away.

00:16:28.884 --> 00:16:33.263
You're the one who nudged me
And asked me out, aha

00:16:33.347 --> 00:16:36.850
I'm not the one who nudged you
And asked you out, aha

00:16:36.934 --> 00:16:37.935
SEO MI-RAE

00:16:38.018 --> 00:16:39.770
You lied to me all the time

00:16:39.853 --> 00:16:43.774
Saying you couldn't pick up my calls
Because your phone died

00:16:43.857 --> 00:16:45.734
I hate you so much, aha

00:16:45.818 --> 00:16:48.821
Say no more
And just hang up the phone

00:16:48.904 --> 00:16:50.989
Hang up!
I don't want to talk…

00:16:51.073 --> 00:16:54.034
Ms. Yun, why won't you answer your phone?

00:16:54.701 --> 00:16:57.538
My phone is crying, and so am I

00:16:57.621 --> 00:17:00.082
Holy crap! What the hell?

00:17:00.165 --> 00:17:02.334
-What are you doing?
-Come outside.

00:17:02.417 --> 00:17:04.753
You're hurting me! That hurts!

00:17:04.837 --> 00:17:05.671
Seriously!

00:17:07.005 --> 00:17:08.590
Are you out of your mind?

00:17:08.674 --> 00:17:11.426
Hey, how did you know where to find me?

00:17:11.510 --> 00:17:13.887
Your destinations are so predictable.

00:17:13.971 --> 00:17:16.557
Do you even know
what situation you're in right now?

00:17:16.640 --> 00:17:17.766
Yeah.

00:17:17.850 --> 00:17:19.268
Then what are you doing here?

00:17:20.144 --> 00:17:21.687
You're one to talk.

00:17:21.770 --> 00:17:24.356
You should've dealt with
the office politics for me.

00:17:24.439 --> 00:17:26.525
When they told you
he'd be moving to Friday,

00:17:26.608 --> 00:17:29.153
were you just standing there
with your arms wide open?

00:17:29.236 --> 00:17:30.320
That…

00:17:30.404 --> 00:17:33.323
It was so sudden.
I couldn't do anything about it.

00:17:33.407 --> 00:17:35.242
For the love of…

00:17:35.325 --> 00:17:37.661
First place? Fine, let him have it!

00:17:37.744 --> 00:17:39.037
What?

00:17:39.121 --> 00:17:41.665
Ms. Yun, you can't do that.

00:17:41.748 --> 00:17:44.710
Why not?
It's not like it would affect you much.

00:17:44.793 --> 00:17:47.629
Excuse me?
What do you mean, it wouldn't affect me?

00:17:47.713 --> 00:17:51.175
If your place drops the moment
I start working with you, what would Park…

00:17:51.675 --> 00:17:55.721
I mean, what would people out there
say about me?

00:17:56.346 --> 00:18:00.058
Plus, this kid had the nerve
to claw his way onto the same day as you

00:18:00.142 --> 00:18:01.768
to steal your spotlight.

00:18:01.852 --> 00:18:03.562
Shit.

00:18:03.645 --> 00:18:07.065
Are you really going to let him
get his way this easily?

00:18:07.149 --> 00:18:09.234
Damn it, seriously!

00:18:15.616 --> 00:18:17.159
This is driving me crazy.

00:18:18.785 --> 00:18:19.703
Thank you.

00:18:21.246 --> 00:18:23.624
Is it okay if I head out now--

00:18:24.458 --> 00:18:25.918
So freaking agonizing.

00:18:27.502 --> 00:18:29.963
So-yeong, you can go home now.

00:18:30.047 --> 00:18:30.881
Right.

00:18:34.885 --> 00:18:39.514
I feel like we'll come up with something
if we think just a little harder.

00:18:40.098 --> 00:18:42.893
-Got it.
-Oh, she's got it.

00:18:48.482 --> 00:18:49.608
Ms. Yun!

00:18:49.691 --> 00:18:53.654
We really need something new to happen
to Choi Si-woo right now.

00:18:53.737 --> 00:18:57.699
Define "new" for me. You said you weren't
a fan of his aunt kicking up a storm.

00:19:01.370 --> 00:19:03.372
My brain isn't working either.

00:19:06.333 --> 00:19:07.793
Should I kill off Choi Si-woo?

00:19:07.876 --> 00:19:11.546
If the main character dies,
everyone will come flocking, won't they?

00:19:12.756 --> 00:19:15.259
Please stop talking nonsense.

00:19:15.801 --> 00:19:16.969
Tell me.

00:19:17.594 --> 00:19:20.514
Why do you think TMTK became
my most successful work?

00:19:22.266 --> 00:19:23.767
Well, that's…

00:19:23.850 --> 00:19:27.521
That's because it allowed your talents
to truly shine.

00:19:28.230 --> 00:19:29.398
What are my talents?

00:19:30.524 --> 00:19:35.988
Well, you're really good
at drawing handsome men.

00:19:38.407 --> 00:19:39.866
Therein lies the problem.

00:19:40.617 --> 00:19:42.494
That was the problem from the start.

00:19:42.577 --> 00:19:45.080
It wasn't supposed to be a hit,

00:19:45.580 --> 00:19:48.250
but it came this far
because Choi Si-woo was too handsome.

00:19:48.834 --> 00:19:51.128
Choi Si-woo's looks are so immaculate

00:19:51.211 --> 00:19:55.299
that people can't stop reading
this incredibly boring slog!

00:19:55.382 --> 00:19:57.467
All because Choi Si-woo is too handsome!

00:19:58.051 --> 00:19:59.011
Seriously!

00:19:59.094 --> 00:20:02.848
I think I'm starting to understand
why Producer Cho left the company.

00:20:02.931 --> 00:20:03.932
Honestly,

00:20:05.100 --> 00:20:06.685
I want to end this series.

00:20:07.311 --> 00:20:09.313
I'm so sick and tired of it!

00:20:09.938 --> 00:20:10.772
Seo.

00:20:11.773 --> 00:20:13.859
Please save me.

00:20:15.777 --> 00:20:19.239
My whole life is falling apart.

00:20:25.245 --> 00:20:26.913
YOUR DAILY WARMTH, A PERFECT MOMENT

00:20:26.997 --> 00:20:29.541
Enjoying yourself?
We're dying here, you know.

00:20:29.624 --> 00:20:31.251
Do you think he really likes me?

00:20:31.335 --> 00:20:32.502
Hey, stop it.

00:20:32.586 --> 00:20:36.381
You've been talking about him all day.
Do you like him that much?

00:20:36.465 --> 00:20:39.092
It's just that he won't give me
a clear answer.

00:20:39.176 --> 00:20:41.803
Just go and ask him
if he actually likes you.

00:20:42.387 --> 00:20:44.097
Let's go ask him right now.

00:20:44.181 --> 00:20:45.015
Right now?

00:20:48.935 --> 00:20:52.272
Just go and ask him
if he actually likes you.

00:20:52.773 --> 00:20:55.025
Let's go ask him right now.

00:20:59.237 --> 00:21:02.157
Let's go ask him. Let's go. Just ask him.

00:21:02.240 --> 00:21:03.325
Let's ask. Should we?

00:21:03.408 --> 00:21:04.284
Let's go ask him.

00:21:04.368 --> 00:21:06.203
Just ask him. Should we go ask him?

00:21:06.286 --> 00:21:07.829
Let's ask him.

00:21:07.913 --> 00:21:09.456
Ask him.

00:21:24.846 --> 00:21:25.931
Come in.

00:21:27.557 --> 00:21:28.934
What? Where am I?

00:21:34.898 --> 00:21:38.068
What's this?
Why did you call me to your room?

00:21:40.445 --> 00:21:41.988
Too many eyes watching outside.

00:21:43.115 --> 00:21:44.032
I didn't see anyone.

00:21:47.285 --> 00:21:49.162
The moment I step out, they'll swarm.

00:21:51.498 --> 00:21:54.668
Hang in there.
Think about why you came here.

00:21:55.168 --> 00:21:56.128
What's with that look?

00:21:58.255 --> 00:21:59.506
But I must say,

00:22:00.924 --> 00:22:03.009
he's just so damn handsome.

00:22:06.304 --> 00:22:07.764
I have something to say--

00:22:07.848 --> 00:22:09.474
I believe you were a supervisor?

00:22:09.975 --> 00:22:11.893
-Don't come in starting tomorrow.
-What?

00:22:11.977 --> 00:22:13.228
Stop coming in to work.

00:22:15.605 --> 00:22:18.358
Wait, are you firing me right now?

00:22:18.442 --> 00:22:20.026
You could say that.

00:22:20.527 --> 00:22:22.154
I don't date company employees.

00:22:23.196 --> 00:22:24.781
If I'm to date you,

00:22:25.615 --> 00:22:26.867
I have to fire you.

00:22:30.245 --> 00:22:32.164
He's oblivious to labor laws.

00:22:33.039 --> 00:22:34.791
Why is he addressing me informally?

00:22:35.375 --> 00:22:36.376
Anything to say?

00:22:38.879 --> 00:22:43.008
I'm guessing every girl
you've ever asked out has said yes,

00:22:43.675 --> 00:22:45.260
but I'm not like that.

00:22:45.343 --> 00:22:47.512
-So?
-Show some effort.

00:22:47.596 --> 00:22:49.264
Show me what you're made of.

00:23:00.942 --> 00:23:03.069
You're more intriguing than I thought.

00:23:04.654 --> 00:23:07.866
It sounds like you want me to seduce you.
Is that right?

00:23:08.533 --> 00:23:11.453
Yes, seduce me.
Show me how it's done right now!

00:23:11.536 --> 00:23:13.455
I'm in a hurry. We don't have much time.

00:23:13.538 --> 00:23:15.207
On second thought, I won't fire you.

00:23:15.290 --> 00:23:18.251
No! You have to fire me.
Didn't you want to date me?

00:23:18.335 --> 00:23:22.130
I think I'll keep my eye on you
a bit longer.

00:23:23.048 --> 00:23:24.925
Don't do that! I told you I'm in a hurry.

00:23:25.675 --> 00:23:26.843
Yes, Mr. Choi.

00:23:27.886 --> 00:23:29.012
Choi.

00:23:34.017 --> 00:23:35.644
Reassign her to the secretary's office.

00:23:35.727 --> 00:23:36.728
Yes, sir.

00:23:36.811 --> 00:23:37.646
What is this now?

00:23:52.452 --> 00:23:54.120
-Aren't you leaving?
-What?

00:23:54.204 --> 00:23:55.956
I'm done talking. Leave now.

00:23:58.416 --> 00:23:59.584
What even…

00:24:32.742 --> 00:24:34.828
Allow me to introduce myself first.

00:24:34.911 --> 00:24:36.413
I'm the chief secretary,

00:24:36.496 --> 00:24:39.416
assisting the general manager
day and night, right by his side.

00:24:39.916 --> 00:24:43.253
My name is Choi Min-ju.

00:24:43.336 --> 00:24:45.130
CHIEF SECRETARY
CHOI MIN-JU

00:24:45.213 --> 00:24:47.048
As I'm sure you know,

00:24:47.632 --> 00:24:51.511
the secretary's office at SY Group
is a demanding department.

00:24:52.429 --> 00:24:54.806
Though you may have parachuted in,
Mr. Choi insists

00:24:54.889 --> 00:24:58.810
we follow at least the basic protocol,
so he specifically asked me

00:24:59.311 --> 00:25:01.980
to carry out a simple job interview.

00:25:02.480 --> 00:25:04.399
An interview? My interview?

00:25:04.482 --> 00:25:07.485
Yes. I simply need your honest answers.

00:25:07.569 --> 00:25:09.070
What is your favorite food?

00:25:09.154 --> 00:25:09.988
Food?

00:25:11.865 --> 00:25:15.619
I… Well, I like beef and pork.

00:25:15.702 --> 00:25:16.661
BEEF, PORK

00:25:17.245 --> 00:25:20.081
And… I just like all kinds of meat.

00:25:20.165 --> 00:25:21.124
What about hobbies?

00:25:21.207 --> 00:25:23.668
What kind of date would you like to go on?

00:25:23.752 --> 00:25:25.837
Where would you like to travel?

00:25:29.174 --> 00:25:31.801
-Is this really an interview?
-What is your ideal type?

00:25:32.969 --> 00:25:36.139
He should be asking me himself.
Why is he having others do it?

00:25:36.222 --> 00:25:37.849
Excuse me.

00:25:40.602 --> 00:25:42.062
Yes, Mr. Choi?

00:25:42.145 --> 00:25:43.188
Yes.

00:25:43.271 --> 00:25:44.272
I see.

00:25:44.773 --> 00:25:46.941
Allergies and shoe size.

00:25:47.442 --> 00:25:49.069
Yes, I'll check right away.

00:25:49.569 --> 00:25:51.488
Yes, I'll be right there.

00:25:52.572 --> 00:25:55.075
Mr. Ko! Why haven't we left yet?

00:25:55.659 --> 00:25:57.285
There's a car blocking us.

00:25:58.912 --> 00:26:01.206
Mr. Choi insists that we hurry along.

00:26:01.289 --> 00:26:03.124
Not going anywhere, are you?

00:26:04.918 --> 00:26:06.836
Hey! My apologies.

00:26:06.920 --> 00:26:08.546
This really brings me back.

00:26:09.047 --> 00:26:11.299
Hey! You punk!

00:26:13.510 --> 00:26:15.387
I'm going to take care of it.

00:26:17.847 --> 00:26:18.723
Hey!

00:26:19.683 --> 00:26:22.686
Wait, is that really necessary?

00:26:22.769 --> 00:26:24.062
-It's okay.
-Hey!

00:26:24.145 --> 00:26:25.855
Mr. Ko isn't your average person.

00:26:31.611 --> 00:26:32.821
Taken care of.

00:26:38.576 --> 00:26:41.705
Did they really need to include this part
from the webtoon?

00:26:45.875 --> 00:26:48.628
Ms. Seo, Mr. Choi would like to see you.

00:26:50.422 --> 00:26:51.423
This way, please.

00:26:56.428 --> 00:26:57.971
Mr. Choi

00:26:58.680 --> 00:27:00.765
does not like it when people knock twice.

00:27:01.391 --> 00:27:03.560
Going forward, when you're knocking,

00:27:03.643 --> 00:27:07.063
a single gentle tap will suffice.

00:27:09.524 --> 00:27:11.359
-This is ridiculous.
-Excuse me?

00:27:13.027 --> 00:27:13.903
Nothing.

00:27:14.404 --> 00:27:16.990
Why don't you give it a try? A gentle tap.

00:27:17.073 --> 00:27:18.199
A gentle tap.

00:27:24.330 --> 00:27:25.415
Come in.

00:27:25.957 --> 00:27:26.791
You may enter.

00:27:26.875 --> 00:27:30.044
By the way, that was a little too loud.

00:27:33.047 --> 00:27:36.217
That annoying woman.
She's just like in the webtoon.

00:27:56.780 --> 00:27:57.989
What is all this?

00:27:59.616 --> 00:28:00.450
Flowers.

00:28:01.534 --> 00:28:03.411
The best way to win a woman over.

00:28:06.456 --> 00:28:08.875
Hey! You shouldn't have.

00:28:11.753 --> 00:28:12.837
Look.

00:28:13.546 --> 00:28:18.301
I may be seducing you, but I expect
a bit more respect from you than "hey."

00:28:26.142 --> 00:28:27.560
So? Do you like it?

00:28:29.979 --> 00:28:30.814
Kinda.

00:28:32.482 --> 00:28:33.399
You're picky.

00:28:39.489 --> 00:28:41.449
So, what's next?

00:28:42.283 --> 00:28:43.910
There's got to be a next step.

00:28:43.993 --> 00:28:45.745
You have it all prepared, don't you?

00:28:50.583 --> 00:28:52.627
How could someone be so shameless?

00:28:54.963 --> 00:28:56.297
You didn't prepare a date?

00:28:57.382 --> 00:28:59.133
Come with me.

00:29:06.850 --> 00:29:07.684
This is weak.

00:29:08.768 --> 00:29:09.769
What?

00:29:10.270 --> 00:29:13.189
I said this is weak.
This will never satisfy our read…

00:29:13.273 --> 00:29:16.109
I mean, do you think this will satisfy me?

00:29:16.693 --> 00:29:18.027
What are you talking about?

00:29:18.528 --> 00:29:19.779
It hasn't even started yet.

00:29:42.677 --> 00:29:44.804
I figured you should eat
before we go on a date.

00:29:45.471 --> 00:29:46.347
Try it.

00:29:53.521 --> 00:29:56.024
It actually tastes like food!

00:29:57.233 --> 00:29:58.067
No way.

00:30:12.707 --> 00:30:15.710
How did I end up owing my life
to a woman like that?

00:30:22.425 --> 00:30:24.218
A sudden trip to the department store?

00:30:25.637 --> 00:30:26.471
Are you…

00:30:27.931 --> 00:30:31.851
Given my social standing, I can't take you
on a date without stopping by here first.

00:30:32.810 --> 00:30:33.937
Oh my God!

00:30:44.405 --> 00:30:45.239
Go on.

00:30:45.740 --> 00:30:46.991
Try them on.

00:30:57.877 --> 00:30:58.711
Whoa.

00:30:58.795 --> 00:30:59.921
Would you like to try it on?

00:31:00.004 --> 00:31:00.838
YES

00:31:22.276 --> 00:31:23.319
Do you like it?

00:31:37.750 --> 00:31:41.295
Why would you rent the entire pool
if you're not going to swim?

00:31:41.379 --> 00:31:43.172
Why? Do you not approve?

00:31:44.090 --> 00:31:45.216
It's not bad.

00:31:52.432 --> 00:31:53.433
Seo Mi-rae.

00:32:03.234 --> 00:32:05.153
What do you think? Do you like it?

00:32:08.656 --> 00:32:09.824
Not sure.

00:32:10.450 --> 00:32:12.285
I think I might like it.

00:32:39.395 --> 00:32:40.646
You're late.

00:32:52.825 --> 00:32:53.993
I get it now.

00:32:55.286 --> 00:32:56.120
This

00:32:57.080 --> 00:32:58.498
isn't a cliché, but…

00:33:01.209 --> 00:33:03.503
Ms. Yun! Open up!

00:33:05.088 --> 00:33:06.380
You know what time it is?

00:33:06.464 --> 00:33:08.341
Ms. Yun, I got it.

00:33:08.424 --> 00:33:09.509
-I got it!
-Got what?

00:33:10.802 --> 00:33:12.804
I realized what Choi Si-woo needs to do.

00:33:12.887 --> 00:33:13.805
What?

00:33:14.430 --> 00:33:16.349
Let's go back to the beginning.

00:33:16.432 --> 00:33:17.266
The beginning?

00:33:17.350 --> 00:33:21.354
You said this webtoon could become a hit
because of Si-woo's handsome looks.

00:33:21.437 --> 00:33:22.271
I did.

00:33:22.355 --> 00:33:25.900
Plus, the fantasy of him being a chaebol
who can give you everything you want.

00:33:25.983 --> 00:33:29.445
But you said people are hating on it
because the chaebol thing was so cliché.

00:33:29.529 --> 00:33:31.114
No, I was wrong.

00:33:31.697 --> 00:33:32.907
-You were wrong?
-Listen.

00:33:32.990 --> 00:33:36.661
Choi Si-woo is not a cliché.
He's a classic.

00:33:37.245 --> 00:33:40.081
The definition of classic
that female readers desire.

00:33:40.164 --> 00:33:42.500
Women were raving about TMTK

00:33:42.583 --> 00:33:44.961
for offering an escape
from their harsh reality,

00:33:45.044 --> 00:33:49.799
but all those cheesy lines you gave Si-woo
ended up giving them the ick.

00:33:50.383 --> 00:33:51.342
So what's your point?

00:33:51.968 --> 00:33:53.511
We've totally got this.

00:33:54.095 --> 00:33:58.099
Let's get back to the drawing board
and give them a true chaebol romance.

00:34:01.185 --> 00:34:03.729
First, the department store.
Let's start there.

00:34:03.813 --> 00:34:05.022
-Yeah?
-The luxury floor.

00:34:05.106 --> 00:34:05.940
The luxury floor?

00:34:08.276 --> 00:34:12.405
Seeing Si-woo suddenly lose his composure
really made my heart flutter…

00:34:12.905 --> 00:34:14.323
I mean, I'm saying it would.

00:34:14.407 --> 00:34:16.325
-So, pull up his top?
-So-yeong.

00:34:16.409 --> 00:34:18.911
We could use some darker coloring here.

00:34:18.995 --> 00:34:21.038
-And the ring.
-The ring?

00:34:21.122 --> 00:34:23.249
-The ring is too small.
-It needs to be bigger?

00:34:23.332 --> 00:34:25.334
At least this big.

00:34:25.418 --> 00:34:26.794
You heard her. Leave it to me.

00:34:26.878 --> 00:34:29.547
Si-woo comes over, grabs her wrist,
and drags her away.

00:34:29.630 --> 00:34:31.257
She will feel a vibe.

00:34:31.340 --> 00:34:33.426
Game over. Classic.

00:34:41.017 --> 00:34:42.727
EUN NA-RA, SHINE FOR ME, BY MY SIDE

00:35:07.793 --> 00:35:10.046
-Here to buy coffee?
-Yes.

00:35:10.129 --> 00:35:11.797
Iced latte, please.

00:35:11.881 --> 00:35:14.467
One iced latte. That will be 5,000 won.

00:35:26.646 --> 00:35:29.065
We'll be working late together
before every deadline.

00:35:30.858 --> 00:35:31.692
I guess.

00:35:37.323 --> 00:35:38.532
You know I didn't mean to.

00:35:39.617 --> 00:35:42.495
You make it sound
like it was a car accident.

00:35:43.579 --> 00:35:45.164
You seem mad at me. That's why.

00:35:46.332 --> 00:35:47.291
I'm not.

00:35:47.375 --> 00:35:48.501
Doors opening.

00:35:57.009 --> 00:35:59.971
Is that your habit? Putting on a front?

00:36:01.931 --> 00:36:03.766
Doors closing.

00:36:04.433 --> 00:36:07.853
It shows, anyway.
You're terrible at keeping a poker face.

00:36:10.398 --> 00:36:11.649
-Is that right?
-Yes.

00:36:12.233 --> 00:36:14.860
Then why ask me, you jerk?

00:36:18.906 --> 00:36:21.242
I guess you'll also be here for a while.

00:36:22.076 --> 00:36:23.577
-Me?
-Yes.

00:36:23.661 --> 00:36:25.162
I noticed you had two cups of coffee.

00:36:26.998 --> 00:36:30.501
I got another one while the café was open
so I can have it on my way home.

00:36:30.584 --> 00:36:32.336
It tastes bad when the ice melts.

00:36:32.420 --> 00:36:35.423
I know. I plan on clocking out
before the ice melts.

00:36:36.966 --> 00:36:38.551
Doors opening.

00:36:40.678 --> 00:36:41.679
Me too.

00:37:04.160 --> 00:37:05.369
1 MESSAGE

00:37:05.453 --> 00:37:06.787
Damn it.

00:37:17.840 --> 00:37:18.758
Shit.

00:37:19.884 --> 00:37:21.802
Are you kidding me?

00:37:24.930 --> 00:37:27.308
No. I shouldn't nag her.

00:37:29.143 --> 00:37:30.478
Don't you nag her.

00:37:37.985 --> 00:37:39.195
Come on!

00:37:43.657 --> 00:37:44.658
YUN SONG
&lt;TMTK&gt; E110

00:37:48.788 --> 00:37:49.705
It's over.

00:38:01.467 --> 00:38:03.177
By now…

00:38:12.645 --> 00:38:13.979
3: PlanC
HWANY

00:38:14.772 --> 00:38:16.273
1: THE MAN TO KNOW
YUN SONG

00:38:19.860 --> 00:38:22.029
First place!

00:38:22.530 --> 00:38:24.156
First place!

00:38:24.240 --> 00:38:27.576
First place, first place
First place is mine

00:38:27.660 --> 00:38:31.288
First place
It doesn't change hands easily

00:38:40.631 --> 00:38:41.966
Congratulations, Mi-rae!

00:38:42.049 --> 00:38:43.259
Congratulations!

00:38:43.342 --> 00:38:44.343
-Congrats!
-Hello.

00:38:44.427 --> 00:38:45.302
Hi.

00:38:46.679 --> 00:38:47.513
Congratulations!

00:38:47.596 --> 00:38:48.973
Congratulations!

00:38:57.648 --> 00:38:59.150
Seo Mi-rae!

00:39:00.109 --> 00:39:01.026
Hi.

00:39:01.110 --> 00:39:01.986
Morning!

00:39:03.571 --> 00:39:04.405
Oh dear.

00:39:05.239 --> 00:39:06.824
Who turned you around?

00:39:19.587 --> 00:39:20.421
Well defended.

00:39:23.674 --> 00:39:25.301
Did something happen?

00:39:27.094 --> 00:39:29.346
Hey, did something happen here?

00:39:36.270 --> 00:39:37.521
Let's get to work, okay?

00:39:43.319 --> 00:39:44.737
Nailed it, Yun Song!

00:39:44.820 --> 00:39:46.363
She's finally back on track.

00:39:46.447 --> 00:39:48.157
She poured her soul into this one.

00:39:48.240 --> 00:39:49.742
A triumphant return for TMTK!

00:39:50.242 --> 00:39:52.786
"Hella fun"? I wouldn't go that far.

00:40:08.177 --> 00:40:09.595
Good times.

00:40:56.100 --> 00:40:58.811
It's only a dinner.
Did you have to bring a private jet?

00:40:58.894 --> 00:41:00.062
Don't approve of this either?

00:41:02.189 --> 00:41:03.774
What took you so long?

00:41:05.651 --> 00:41:08.404
I have to stick to my hours.
I'm just an employee, after all.

00:41:09.321 --> 00:41:11.949
You make your boss wait,
then use work as an excuse?

00:41:14.159 --> 00:41:15.828
Where are we having dinner tonight?

00:41:15.911 --> 00:41:17.329
You'll see. Come with me.

00:41:31.969 --> 00:41:32.845
Look!

00:41:35.055 --> 00:41:36.056
Dolphins!

00:42:02.916 --> 00:42:05.252
Let's get engaged. I'll handle my parents.

00:42:07.880 --> 00:42:08.881
Engaged?

00:42:09.923 --> 00:42:10.758
Are you mad?

00:42:12.343 --> 00:42:14.720
You answered a chaebol's proposal
with a spit take?

00:42:16.430 --> 00:42:19.475
Didn't I tell you?
We're just dating, nothing more.

00:42:19.558 --> 00:42:20.643
What?

00:42:22.645 --> 00:42:24.355
I told you not to fall for me.

00:42:58.222 --> 00:42:59.390
It's so pretty.

00:43:05.562 --> 00:43:06.689
Mi-rae.

00:43:07.272 --> 00:43:08.107
Yeah?

00:43:08.816 --> 00:43:09.775
Let's do it your way.

00:43:10.693 --> 00:43:11.527
My way?

00:43:12.611 --> 00:43:14.613
We don't have to get engaged.

00:43:18.617 --> 00:43:19.785
In exchange…

00:43:22.037 --> 00:43:24.707
can you at least be my girlfriend?

00:43:31.255 --> 00:43:33.424
I've never asked anyone
for anything before.

00:43:55.320 --> 00:43:56.363
Do I have to

00:43:57.865 --> 00:43:59.283
ask for this too?

00:44:02.995 --> 00:44:04.455
Is he…

00:44:05.038 --> 00:44:05.873
What…

00:44:25.184 --> 00:44:27.895
Dopamine overload!

00:44:45.579 --> 00:44:46.872
Why look away?

00:44:48.540 --> 00:44:49.458
Did I?

00:44:53.086 --> 00:44:54.129
I got something.

00:45:07.768 --> 00:45:11.104
I'm giving this to you as a boyfriend,
so don't turn it down.

00:45:11.605 --> 00:45:12.606
That's all it means.

00:45:14.191 --> 00:45:15.275
Si-woo!

00:45:49.768 --> 00:45:51.603
Oh my God!

00:46:07.160 --> 00:46:07.995
What?

00:46:08.078 --> 00:46:09.121
What's going on?

00:46:16.712 --> 00:46:17.838
What's happening?

00:46:18.881 --> 00:46:19.715
Hello!

00:46:21.592 --> 00:46:25.596
Ms. Seo Mi-rae, your 50 hours
of dating Choi Si-woo have ended.

00:46:25.679 --> 00:46:26.722
What did you say?

00:46:26.805 --> 00:46:28.098
SERVICE PERIOD EXPIRED

00:46:28.181 --> 00:46:29.182
No!

00:46:30.225 --> 00:46:31.393
Si-woo!

00:46:32.019 --> 00:46:33.186
Damn it!

00:46:40.319 --> 00:46:41.320
What was that?

00:46:51.747 --> 00:46:54.666
"You can only date a male character
for up to 50 hours"?

00:46:58.086 --> 00:46:59.004
No.

00:47:00.672 --> 00:47:01.673
No.

00:47:01.757 --> 00:47:04.134
No!

00:47:05.010 --> 00:47:06.970
We have a meeting with Mipare tomorrow.

00:47:07.054 --> 00:47:11.433
Okay. Both of them are on the rise,
so we must sign their upcoming titles.

00:47:11.516 --> 00:47:12.726
-Yes, sir!
-And Team 1?

00:47:12.809 --> 00:47:14.978
I contacted Hwan-su,

00:47:15.729 --> 00:47:19.024
but they want to finish the series first,
so that's on hold for now.

00:47:19.107 --> 00:47:21.360
Choi Si-woo left a lasting impression.

00:47:25.072 --> 00:47:26.365
What?

00:47:28.951 --> 00:47:30.118
God!

00:47:30.202 --> 00:47:32.704
So much so
that he threw my life off balance.

00:47:34.748 --> 00:47:36.875
Looks that surpass
his webtoon counterpart,

00:47:36.959 --> 00:47:39.711
great conversation skills,
and subtle thoughtfulness.

00:47:39.795 --> 00:47:41.922
It was definitely too much…

00:47:53.225 --> 00:47:55.435
and yet, his sexiness made it all okay.

00:47:56.728 --> 00:47:58.063
Hella sexy.

00:47:58.146 --> 00:48:04.152
HELLA SEXY

00:48:04.820 --> 00:48:06.863
DEVICE SATISFACTION
USER EXPERIENCE REVIEW

00:48:08.156 --> 00:48:11.827
As expected from a producer,
it's a very well-written review.

00:48:12.369 --> 00:48:13.203
That's a relief.

00:48:13.286 --> 00:48:16.999
It's fascinating that you got matched
with a character from one of your works.

00:48:17.082 --> 00:48:19.209
So how was it?
Tell me what you really think.

00:48:20.794 --> 00:48:22.546
What exactly do you mean?

00:48:23.338 --> 00:48:26.591
I just want to hear your honest opinion.

00:48:29.511 --> 00:48:32.514
It was fun. Well, more than fun.

00:48:33.849 --> 00:48:35.726
Then why did you end it so soon?

00:48:37.019 --> 00:48:40.355
I think I've experienced enough
to understand what it's about,

00:48:40.439 --> 00:48:44.026
and Choi Si-woo set the bar
way too high from the get-go, so…

00:48:46.278 --> 00:48:47.237
Ms. Seo.

00:48:48.030 --> 00:48:48.864
Yes?

00:48:48.947 --> 00:48:51.575
There are still 899 characters left.

00:48:51.658 --> 00:48:53.869
What makes you so sure
Si-woo is the best one?

00:48:57.247 --> 00:49:01.752
If you throw away your remaining hours,
you might regret it later on.

00:49:08.300 --> 00:49:13.638
I think she knows she probably shouldn't,
but she can't help being drawn in.

00:49:14.473 --> 00:49:15.640
Who is he?

00:49:16.141 --> 00:49:18.894
-It's like I'm watching a movie.
-He drives women crazy.

00:49:18.977 --> 00:49:20.979
-Totally.
-Yeah, those eyes…

00:49:21.063 --> 00:49:22.981
He just melts your heart.

00:49:23.065 --> 00:49:25.150
-He draws you in.
-The way he holds her hand!

00:49:25.233 --> 00:49:26.443
Dopamine.

00:49:27.861 --> 00:49:29.905
I need my dopamine!

00:49:41.374 --> 00:49:43.919
There are still 899 characters left.

00:49:44.002 --> 00:49:46.171
What makes you so sure
Si-woo is the best one?

00:49:46.922 --> 00:49:51.051
If you throw away your remaining hours,
you might regret it later on.

00:49:53.470 --> 00:49:54.304
He's right.

00:49:54.387 --> 00:49:59.226
It's a one-month subscription trial,
so why don't I make full use of that?

00:50:00.560 --> 00:50:02.646
Since when did I ever turn down freebies?

00:50:03.355 --> 00:50:04.940
Stop kidding yourself.

00:51:13.133 --> 00:51:15.969
Looks like you've lucked out
on another amazing pick today.

00:51:17.470 --> 00:51:18.305
Hurry along now.

00:51:19.014 --> 00:51:23.602
I did let Min Jun-young talk me into
returning, but I was still skeptical.

00:51:24.436 --> 00:51:27.564
Could there really be a man more thrilling

00:51:28.064 --> 00:51:31.359
and charming than Choi Si-woo,
a webtoon male lead?

00:51:31.443 --> 00:51:33.278
What's wrong? Is there a problem?

00:51:34.237 --> 00:51:35.655
Give me a second.

00:51:36.448 --> 00:51:38.867
My, you're a handful.

00:51:40.785 --> 00:51:41.620
Now…

00:51:47.792 --> 00:51:49.294
Hey, don't push…

00:52:51.940 --> 00:52:53.775
But once again,

00:52:54.859 --> 00:52:58.238
Boyfriend on Demand managed
to far exceed my expectations.

00:55:57.459 --> 00:56:02.464
Subtitle translation by: Daham Yoon